<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Wee Harvester Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Head to Western Karana and follow C. Miller through the fields until he drops a bail of hay.<BR>
<BR>
2) Head to Feerrott and find Roror.  He is usually relatively close to the Rathe Mountains.  Hail him, and then give him the Hay and 66gp.   He will give you back some Cursed Hay.<BR>
<BR>
3) Head to North Qeynos and visit the Temple of Life.  As you head towards the temple there will some NPCs on your right.  The one on the far left is the one who gives the blessed oil quest.  Hail him and get the blessed oil.<BR>
<BR>
4) Head to a forge and put the blessed oil and the cursed hay into it.  Combine.  This has been known to fail if you have low smithing skill.  If you are successful you receive Writhing Hay.<BR>
<BR>
5) Head to Rivervale and give the Writhing Hay to Shakey the Scarecrow to receive either the Wee Harvester or the Belt of the River.</div>
<BR>
